                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素伤害</span>，对所有后台角色造成1点<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">穿透伤害</span>，召唤<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">冰灵珠</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/01/47826599/6b78c979575a782c1625dce67992cf90_6722266871834274637.png",
